Java 8 introduce for concise code and functional programming like scala and python
New features
1. Lambda expressions(anonymous functions)
2. Stream API
3. Default methods in interface(Can't override methods form object class)
4. Static methods
5. Functional interfaces
6. Optional
7. Method reference and constructor reference(Code reusable)
8. Date API
9. Nashorn and Java script engine

Advantages
1 concise code
2 more readable and reusable
3 more testable
4 parallel operations


